WEBVTT

00:01:08.945 --> 00:01:10.105
Her name's Lin?

00:01:10.625 --> 00:01:12.225
Beautiful name.

00:01:12.305 --> 00:01:13.665
And she has a pretty face.

00:01:13.745 --> 00:01:14.985
She's kind too.

00:01:15.585 --> 00:01:17.465
Can't believe
someone like her actually exists.

00:01:18.585 --> 00:01:19.665
It's okay. I'll pick it up for you.

00:01:25.625 --> 00:01:27.985
I'm focusing my mind to meditate

00:01:28.505 --> 00:01:30.185
so that my mind may be at peace.

00:01:30.265 --> 00:01:32.865
Ugh, why didn't it help?

00:01:32.945 --> 00:01:34.345
-Safe!
-Oh.

00:01:41.985 --> 00:01:43.305
Come and join me for dinner.

00:01:44.105 --> 00:01:45.905
I have something to talk to you about.

00:01:47.465 --> 00:01:49.345
I really admire you.

00:01:49.865 --> 00:01:51.705
I want you…

00:01:53.065 --> 00:01:54.745
I want you…

00:01:55.825 --> 00:01:57.625
to come work with me.

00:01:58.585 --> 00:02:00.505
Someone wants to
take over Play Park's lease.

00:02:00.585 --> 00:02:03.145
Let me see the face of that cruel person.

00:02:09.985 --> 00:02:12.105
Family Nest is going to
sublease this property.

00:02:12.185 --> 00:02:14.305
You were trying to get close to me

00:02:15.305 --> 00:02:17.705
because you knew
I was the manager here, right?

00:02:18.985 --> 00:02:20.545
I can settle the lease agreement

00:02:20.625 --> 00:02:23.145
with Mr. Pao without your help.

00:02:24.225 --> 00:02:25.625
Then go ahead and try.

00:02:26.905 --> 00:02:28.305
Let's see if he'll change his mind.

00:02:32.505 --> 00:02:33.345
Mr. Pao.

00:02:36.585 --> 00:02:38.065
How could you do this?

00:02:39.825 --> 00:02:41.145
Did you already know?

00:02:42.185 --> 00:02:44.185
How long were you planning
to keep this from us?

00:02:47.265 --> 00:02:49.025
When I see your faces,

00:02:49.665 --> 00:02:52.025
I can't bring myself
to shut down Play Park,

00:02:52.105 --> 00:02:54.425
knowing you all have burdens.

00:02:55.385 --> 00:02:57.225
Then you shouldn't let them rent it.

00:02:57.305 --> 00:02:59.945
But you know
the situation with Play Park, right?

00:03:03.305 --> 00:03:04.265
The economy isn't good.

00:03:04.345 --> 00:03:06.825
Sooner or later,
everything will have to change.

00:03:09.625 --> 00:03:11.825
What if we do some marketing?

00:03:11.905 --> 00:03:13.065
If we market it well,

00:03:13.145 --> 00:03:15.385
Play Park could come back
and thrive again. Who knows?

00:03:15.465 --> 00:03:17.905
But my family didn't think so.

00:03:17.985 --> 00:03:20.225
Otherwise, no one
would have told Ms. Lin's father.

00:03:23.665 --> 00:03:25.345
Ms. Lin's been waiting for me long enough.

00:03:27.545 --> 00:03:29.665
How much time do I have
to come to terms with this?

00:04:00.065 --> 00:04:01.985
If you want to make things easy,

00:04:02.065 --> 00:04:03.585
why don't you rent somewhere else?

00:04:21.145 --> 00:04:22.425
Ms. Lin, I'm sorry

00:04:22.505 --> 00:04:23.625
for keeping you waiting.

00:04:23.705 --> 00:04:25.185
It's okay.

00:04:25.825 --> 00:04:28.585
Are you here alone, Ms. Lin?

00:04:28.665 --> 00:04:30.785
Jane is on her way.

00:04:32.065 --> 00:04:32.905
Well…

00:04:32.985 --> 00:04:35.385
I don't know how to start.

00:04:35.465 --> 00:04:37.145
I really don't want to upset you.

00:04:37.225 --> 00:04:40.065
Why don't we reschedule for next week?

00:04:42.545 --> 00:04:43.785
That's good.

00:04:43.865 --> 00:04:46.345
Well, I haven't told the staff yet.

00:04:46.425 --> 00:04:48.705
I'm worried
they won't be able to process it,

00:04:48.785 --> 00:04:51.145
since everything's happening so quickly.

00:04:51.985 --> 00:04:53.345
I understand.

00:04:53.425 --> 00:04:55.305
Play Park wasn't originally in the plan.

00:04:55.385 --> 00:04:57.065
My father just asked to add it.

00:04:57.145 --> 00:04:58.985
Please let the staff know soon.

00:04:59.065 --> 00:05:01.625
If they can resolve their situations
without too much trouble,

00:05:01.705 --> 00:05:03.985
you might find it easier
to make a decision.

00:05:04.665 --> 00:05:05.825
Thank you.

00:05:07.185 --> 00:05:08.705
Please hurry and make it clear.

00:05:08.785 --> 00:05:10.585
Honesty is the most important thing.

00:05:11.345 --> 00:05:13.225
If you let them misunderstand you,

00:05:13.305 --> 00:05:15.705
it might be hard to win their hearts back.

00:05:28.105 --> 00:05:30.225
Ms. Lin. If he keeps
beating around the bush,

00:05:30.305 --> 00:05:32.305
should we have the president
talk to him directly?

00:05:32.385 --> 00:05:35.105
No need. We already have
an appointment next week.

00:05:35.185 --> 00:05:37.345
And you don't need to
report this to Father.

00:05:37.425 --> 00:05:38.705
I'll handle it.

00:05:40.625 --> 00:05:41.625
Yes, ma'am.

00:05:56.145 --> 00:05:57.545
What should I do?

00:06:22.985 --> 00:06:24.145
What now?

00:06:25.305 --> 00:06:26.305
Keep it down.

00:06:29.905 --> 00:06:32.065
Donut just fell asleep.
You want us to be up all night?

00:06:38.345 --> 00:06:41.465
I'm just frustrated.
I can't think of anything.

00:06:49.625 --> 00:06:50.785
Tell me what happened.

00:06:52.465 --> 00:06:55.025
Someone's trying to rent
the Play Park space after Mr. Pao.

00:06:55.665 --> 00:06:56.745
And you know what?

00:06:57.265 --> 00:06:59.105
She was trying to get close to me.

00:06:59.185 --> 00:07:01.945
She's probably scared
I'd rile up the staff.

00:07:02.825 --> 00:07:05.785
So how can she be trusted?

00:07:07.305 --> 00:07:08.945
Good thing she's pretty,

00:07:09.025 --> 00:07:10.505
or I'd be more upset.

00:07:10.585 --> 00:07:11.905
Again?

00:07:12.745 --> 00:07:13.585
A soft spot for pretty ones?

00:07:15.265 --> 00:07:16.225
Watch your mouth.

00:07:16.305 --> 00:07:17.185
Am I wrong?

00:07:17.265 --> 00:07:18.865
Be nice.

00:07:18.945 --> 00:07:20.465
-Am I wrong?
-Stop.

00:07:21.105 --> 00:07:22.105
Still?

00:07:23.265 --> 00:07:24.665
What did I do?

00:07:25.825 --> 00:07:26.985
I just spoke the truth.

00:07:28.865 --> 00:07:29.945
Go for it.

00:07:31.905 --> 00:07:33.785
Just follow your heart.

00:07:37.225 --> 00:07:39.345
And what if you lose your job?

00:07:40.745 --> 00:07:41.785
Whoa.

00:07:41.865 --> 00:07:43.665
I won't lose my job easily.

00:07:44.465 --> 00:07:47.945
You're just an employee.
How can you even fight this?

00:07:49.145 --> 00:07:51.185
If we plan well,

00:07:51.745 --> 00:07:52.905
who knows?

00:07:54.985 --> 00:07:56.385
I think

00:07:56.945 --> 00:07:58.945
we need to play this game two ways.

00:07:59.745 --> 00:08:03.185
First, we need to convince Mr. Pao
to keep fighting.

00:08:03.265 --> 00:08:05.185
Second,

00:08:06.425 --> 00:08:09.025
get Ms. Lin to change her mind
and rent somewhere else instead.

00:08:15.745 --> 00:08:17.305
Is that even possible?

00:08:18.025 --> 00:08:19.225
Why not?

00:08:20.505 --> 00:08:21.545
You know me.

00:08:23.785 --> 00:08:26.025
Alright. I'll get back to work.

00:09:36.705 --> 00:09:37.985
Lilin.

00:09:38.505 --> 00:09:40.745
Wake up. Get it together.

00:09:40.825 --> 00:09:42.585
Note to self. "She's not the one."

00:09:42.665 --> 00:09:44.625
"She has a child. She has a husband."

00:09:44.705 --> 00:09:45.865
"She has a child. She has a husband."

00:09:45.945 --> 00:09:47.825
"She has a child. She has a child."

00:09:47.905 --> 00:09:49.265
"She has a child."

00:10:15.705 --> 00:10:17.025
Oh, Ing?

00:10:17.705 --> 00:10:19.065
What are you doing sitting here?

00:10:23.625 --> 00:10:24.665
Are you crying?

00:10:27.145 --> 00:10:28.225
No, I'm not.

00:10:34.945 --> 00:10:37.065
Are you upset that I'm selling Play Park?

00:10:50.625 --> 00:10:52.065
It worked.

00:10:59.425 --> 00:11:01.105
Get ready, guys.

00:11:01.185 --> 00:11:02.625
He's going in.

00:11:03.385 --> 00:11:04.225
Okay.

00:11:17.025 --> 00:11:19.185
Busy morning, huh?

00:11:25.625 --> 00:11:26.825
What's wrong with them?

00:11:34.425 --> 00:11:36.785
You crushed it,
just like a real diva, Manager.

00:11:36.865 --> 00:11:40.065
Your tears were so convincing,
I actually felt sad too.

00:11:40.145 --> 00:11:41.545
I've got eye drops.

00:11:41.625 --> 00:11:43.585
Manager, will our plan succeed?

00:11:43.665 --> 00:11:45.545
But will he really
not get angry and fire us?

00:11:45.625 --> 00:11:47.425
I gave him side-eye too.

00:11:47.505 --> 00:11:50.665
Oh, he won't fire us.
He's kind and loves us.

00:11:50.745 --> 00:11:53.025
Now that he's seen us
looking like sad dogs,

00:11:53.105 --> 00:11:55.985
he might come to his senses
and change his mind, right?

00:11:56.705 --> 00:11:57.705
Let's cheer up!

00:11:58.665 --> 00:12:00.865
One, two, three, yay!

00:12:00.945 --> 00:12:03.345
Hey, you hungry? You hungry?

00:12:03.425 --> 00:12:04.905
You hungry, or you wanna walk around?

00:12:04.985 --> 00:12:06.345
Or you wanna walk around?

00:12:06.425 --> 00:12:08.905
Or you wanna walk around?

00:12:21.905 --> 00:12:25.065
Have we met before?

00:12:29.065 --> 00:12:30.865
-Wow!
-The sound.

00:12:32.785 --> 00:12:34.745
No, I don't think so.

00:12:38.785 --> 00:12:41.105
You're funny.

00:12:49.065 --> 00:12:49.905
What's your name?

00:12:50.505 --> 00:12:52.625
"My name's Donut."

00:12:53.225 --> 00:12:55.465
And my name is Ith.

00:12:58.185 --> 00:12:59.985
Your son is really cute.

00:13:02.265 --> 00:13:04.865
No, he's my nephew.

00:13:05.465 --> 00:13:06.345
Nephew?

00:13:06.425 --> 00:13:08.465
Yes. He's my sister's son.

00:13:12.265 --> 00:13:14.545
But I am…

00:13:15.345 --> 00:13:17.665
still single.

00:13:20.865 --> 00:13:22.385
Good for you.

00:13:22.465 --> 00:13:24.785
So his dad didn't come with you guys?

00:13:25.425 --> 00:13:28.225
He won't come.
They divorced a long time ago.

00:13:36.545 --> 00:13:38.025
Please excuse me then.

00:13:38.865 --> 00:13:39.825
Right.

00:13:40.865 --> 00:13:43.225
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

00:13:45.545 --> 00:13:46.825
Did you see that, Donut?

00:13:46.905 --> 00:13:49.865
I'm still as charming as ever.
A girl just came up to chat.

00:13:50.665 --> 00:13:53.785
Let's go. Let's go. Go, go, go.

00:13:57.465 --> 00:13:58.985
MINI FAN
149 BAHT

00:13:59.065 --> 00:14:00.145
Excuse me.

00:14:00.225 --> 00:14:02.825
Is your boss going to
sublease the Play Park location?

00:14:02.905 --> 00:14:04.545
How did you know that?

00:14:04.625 --> 00:14:06.305
I work in this store.

00:14:06.385 --> 00:14:07.425
I remember you.

00:14:08.025 --> 00:14:10.465
Oh, yes. Is there anything
I can help you with?

00:14:12.585 --> 00:14:14.825
Have you checked the feng shui here?

00:14:14.905 --> 00:14:16.065
Not yet.

00:14:17.905 --> 00:14:19.225
So that's why.

00:14:20.105 --> 00:14:21.185
I'm going now.

00:14:21.265 --> 00:14:22.785
Oh, wait, ma'am.

00:14:22.865 --> 00:14:25.305
You can't just end it
on a cliffhanger like this.

00:14:25.385 --> 00:14:26.625
Oh, come on.

00:14:26.705 --> 00:14:29.065
Please don't make me say any more.

00:14:29.145 --> 00:14:30.505
I'm afraid I'll get fired.

00:14:33.665 --> 00:14:34.785
How about this?

00:14:34.865 --> 00:14:38.385
You can bring in any feng shui expert,

00:14:38.465 --> 00:14:39.825
and you'll understand.

00:14:41.465 --> 00:14:43.145
Where can I find one?

00:14:45.585 --> 00:14:46.545
Ma'am,

00:14:46.625 --> 00:14:49.265
do you know any good feng shui experts?

00:14:56.745 --> 00:14:57.825
Gotcha!

00:15:00.905 --> 00:15:04.305
FREE!
A 100 BAHT GIFT VOUCHER

00:15:23.025 --> 00:15:24.065
Ms. Lin.

00:15:24.145 --> 00:15:26.105
Feng shui is really important, you know.

00:15:26.185 --> 00:15:27.505
Better safe than sorry.

00:15:27.585 --> 00:15:30.065
Even when a lizard warns us,
we have to pay attention.

00:15:30.145 --> 00:15:32.025
Maybe it's just a scam.

00:15:32.705 --> 00:15:34.065
Ms. Lin.

00:15:34.145 --> 00:15:35.385
It won't hurt to let him take a look.

00:15:35.465 --> 00:15:37.425
I've already invited the master.

00:15:37.505 --> 00:15:39.145
Please. Pretty please.

00:15:39.745 --> 00:15:40.905
Then take care of it yourself.

00:15:40.985 --> 00:15:42.825
I'll listen from a distance.

00:15:43.625 --> 00:15:44.985
Okay, Ms. Lin.

00:15:54.665 --> 00:15:57.345
Ms. Lin. Why are you smiling?

00:15:57.425 --> 00:15:58.905
Are you possessed, Ms. Lin?

00:15:58.985 --> 00:16:00.545
Ms. Lin.

00:16:00.625 --> 00:16:01.865
Ms. Lin.

00:16:04.465 --> 00:16:05.505
Uh…

00:16:12.105 --> 00:16:13.185
This place is something.

00:16:21.425 --> 00:16:22.385
-May.
-Yes?

00:16:22.465 --> 00:16:23.825
Go and watch over Mr. Pao.

00:16:23.905 --> 00:16:25.465
If he comes, let me know immediately.

00:16:25.545 --> 00:16:26.745
Yes, Manager.

00:16:26.825 --> 00:16:27.705
-Go.
-I'm out.

00:16:51.345 --> 00:16:54.065
The energy here
is stifling the prime position.

00:16:54.745 --> 00:16:56.905
The entrance and exit are inauspicious.

00:16:57.545 --> 00:16:59.545
In the end,

00:17:00.265 --> 00:17:01.625
the business will stall,

00:17:02.145 --> 00:17:03.665
the income will decline…

00:17:05.545 --> 00:17:07.745
and you will definitely face losses.

00:17:15.704 --> 00:17:16.585
Oh?

00:17:17.184 --> 00:17:18.025
It's you.

00:17:18.105 --> 00:17:19.305
Oh?

00:17:20.224 --> 00:17:22.385
You've met the master before, Ms. Lin?

00:17:22.905 --> 00:17:24.025
In front of the restroom.

00:17:25.665 --> 00:17:28.345
I didn't know you were a feng shui master.

00:17:29.185 --> 00:17:31.225
And where's your nephew?

00:17:32.665 --> 00:17:33.785
He's asleep.

00:17:38.145 --> 00:17:39.345
Please continue, Master.

00:17:39.425 --> 00:17:41.185
Anything else we should be aware of?

00:17:47.065 --> 00:17:47.945
Yes.

00:17:49.745 --> 00:17:52.145
This location is suffering
from a lot of stagnant energy.

00:17:52.225 --> 00:17:53.825
There are many dead spots,

00:17:53.905 --> 00:17:55.345
and the yang energy is unbalanced,

00:17:55.425 --> 00:17:58.145
causing trade to be sluggish

00:17:58.225 --> 00:17:59.865
and business to stagnate.

00:18:00.865 --> 00:18:04.145
So, is there a way to fix this, Master?

00:18:07.465 --> 00:18:08.825
To be honest,

00:18:09.585 --> 00:18:11.705
this place shouldn't be rented.

00:18:11.785 --> 00:18:13.225
Ms. Lin.

00:18:34.305 --> 00:18:35.625
So cute.

00:18:35.705 --> 00:18:37.345
You're so cute, huh?

00:18:38.945 --> 00:18:40.785
-Hm?
-Sis. Sis.

00:18:40.865 --> 00:18:42.785
How was it?

00:18:42.865 --> 00:18:44.105
I was almost caught.

00:18:44.185 --> 00:18:45.185
Oh?

00:18:45.905 --> 00:18:47.025
Why? Weren't you convincing?

00:18:47.105 --> 00:18:50.305
I couldn't have been more convincing.

00:18:50.385 --> 00:18:52.385
But I ran into Ms. Lin
in front of the restroom earlier.

00:18:52.465 --> 00:18:53.385
Huh?

00:18:57.425 --> 00:18:59.585
But she doesn't know
you're my brother, right?

00:19:01.145 --> 00:19:02.385
That face.

00:19:03.025 --> 00:19:05.945
Did you say something weird to her? Huh?

00:19:07.945 --> 00:19:08.825
I just

00:19:09.785 --> 00:19:11.505
told her I'm single.

00:19:12.905 --> 00:19:15.305
You just can't help yourself
around pretty girls, huh?

00:19:15.385 --> 00:19:18.465
Who would have known that was Ms. Lin?

00:19:19.385 --> 00:19:20.825
She's so pretty.

00:19:25.225 --> 00:19:26.065
Why are you smiling?

00:19:27.785 --> 00:19:29.345
-Who's smiling?
-You are.

00:19:29.425 --> 00:19:30.265
I'm not.

00:19:30.865 --> 00:19:32.025
Are you smiling, Donut?

00:19:35.505 --> 00:19:36.905
But they looked convinced, sis.

00:19:36.985 --> 00:19:38.025
Really?

00:19:38.625 --> 00:19:40.105
Especially her secretary.

00:19:40.705 --> 00:19:41.945
And where's Ms. Lin now?

00:19:49.905 --> 00:19:50.745
Jane.

00:19:50.825 --> 00:19:52.385
Wait for me at the car.

00:19:52.465 --> 00:19:53.665
Where are you going?

00:19:53.745 --> 00:19:55.225
I can wait.

00:19:55.305 --> 00:19:56.665
Just go where I told you to go.

00:19:58.105 --> 00:19:58.945
Yes, ma'am.

00:20:16.225 --> 00:20:17.745
Great job, Ith.

00:20:27.945 --> 00:20:28.985
Oh, Ms. Lin?

00:20:30.465 --> 00:20:32.425
I thought you'd already left.

00:20:33.025 --> 00:20:35.225
What are you doing here all alone?

00:20:35.305 --> 00:20:36.425
Just taking a quick break.

00:20:36.505 --> 00:20:38.305
Oh…

00:20:39.065 --> 00:20:41.945
Oh, I heard you brought a feng shui master

00:20:42.025 --> 00:20:43.865
to check the place out, right?

00:20:43.945 --> 00:20:45.225
Mhm.

00:20:47.385 --> 00:20:48.465
Sit here with me.

00:21:10.505 --> 00:21:13.185
You're trying to stop me
from renting this place

00:21:13.265 --> 00:21:15.465
because you know it isn't good, right?

00:21:20.145 --> 00:21:21.265
Mhm.

00:21:22.785 --> 00:21:25.865
Mr. Pao told me
you have a younger brother named Ith.

00:21:29.345 --> 00:21:31.945
Bring your brother to see
the feng shui at my house sometime.

00:21:46.825 --> 00:21:48.025
I…

00:21:49.385 --> 00:21:51.945
I have to get back to work.

00:22:09.705 --> 00:22:10.985
Gus. Praew.

00:22:11.505 --> 00:22:12.505
Have you seen Ith?

00:22:12.585 --> 00:22:13.865
He left.

00:22:13.945 --> 00:22:15.025
He left?

00:22:15.105 --> 00:22:16.545
Just wait until I get home.

00:22:16.625 --> 00:22:17.785
We shouldn't have used him.

00:22:18.385 --> 00:22:19.825
The feng shui plan failed?

00:22:19.905 --> 00:22:21.385
Yes, it did.

00:22:21.465 --> 00:22:23.905
Ms. Lin knows everything now.
What should we do next?

00:22:23.985 --> 00:22:25.945
Oh? I heard that

00:22:26.025 --> 00:22:27.905
the contractor is coming
to see the site tonight.

00:22:27.985 --> 00:22:29.465
Tonight?

00:22:29.545 --> 00:22:30.385
Yes.

00:22:30.465 --> 00:22:33.185
I don't think
Mr. Pao will change his mind.

00:22:33.945 --> 00:22:36.265
We absolutely cannot let them in easily.

00:22:38.705 --> 00:22:39.985
Let me come up with a plan.

00:22:52.185 --> 00:22:53.025
Hey.

00:22:53.105 --> 00:22:54.425
Why aren't all the lights on?

00:22:54.505 --> 00:22:55.385
Yeah.

00:22:56.785 --> 00:22:57.625
Whoa.

00:22:57.705 --> 00:22:59.185
Voice command system?

00:22:59.265 --> 00:23:00.505
That's great.

00:23:00.585 --> 00:23:02.505
Good. That's cool.

00:23:07.025 --> 00:23:08.305
Hey, Pae.

00:23:09.545 --> 00:23:12.105
-I don't think it's right anymore.
-Something's wrong.

00:23:12.185 --> 00:23:13.265
What the hell?

00:23:16.145 --> 00:23:17.345
-Whoa.
-How come?

00:23:17.425 --> 00:23:18.425
That's not good.

00:23:18.505 --> 00:23:20.025
Isn't that strange?

00:23:25.345 --> 00:23:26.785
Oh, crap.

00:23:32.545 --> 00:23:34.025
I think something's really wrong.

00:23:34.105 --> 00:23:35.305
It doesn't look good.

00:23:41.265 --> 00:23:43.505
-Whoa, even weirder.
-Whoa.

00:23:45.225 --> 00:23:46.185
Hey.

00:23:46.265 --> 00:23:47.505
What's happening here?

00:23:55.625 --> 00:23:57.625
-Ghost! Ghost!
-A ghost!

00:24:03.225 --> 00:24:04.665
Pae, let's go!

00:24:04.745 --> 00:24:05.785
-Go!
-No!

00:24:06.545 --> 00:24:07.385
I'm done here!

00:24:13.985 --> 00:24:17.385
Hey, let's show them
the spirit of this land

00:24:17.465 --> 00:24:18.305
is fierce.

00:24:18.385 --> 00:24:20.945
-Must outshine it
-Stop!

00:24:21.025 --> 00:24:23.345
No need to finish the song.

00:24:23.425 --> 00:24:24.585
And where are the workers?

00:24:24.665 --> 00:24:26.145
They're gathering at the parking lot.

00:24:26.945 --> 00:24:28.265
Then here's the next step.

00:24:28.345 --> 00:24:31.185
We'll wait here until they're gone,

00:24:31.265 --> 00:24:32.225
then we'll leave, okay?

00:24:32.305 --> 00:24:33.305
-Okay.
-Okay.

00:24:33.385 --> 00:24:35.105
Ugh, don't swing
your fabulous nails around.

00:24:35.185 --> 00:24:37.385
-Keep them.
-You'd slay too much.

00:24:37.465 --> 00:24:39.705
SECRETARY JANE

00:24:42.985 --> 00:24:44.665
Hello, Ms. Lin.

00:24:44.745 --> 00:24:47.185
The contractor saw a ghost
at the amusement park.

00:24:47.265 --> 00:24:48.705
That's ridiculous.

00:24:48.785 --> 00:24:49.825
You might not be scared,

00:24:49.905 --> 00:24:52.025
but others are.

00:24:52.625 --> 00:24:54.905
I need to rent this place.

00:24:54.985 --> 00:24:57.825
Then I need to find a way to stop you too.

00:24:58.545 --> 00:25:00.825
Should we let them work
during the day instead, Ms. Lin?

00:25:01.425 --> 00:25:03.225
Tell the workers to wait there.

00:25:03.305 --> 00:25:05.505
I'll go see with my own eyes.

00:25:06.025 --> 00:25:08.945
I'd like to see a real ghost once too.

00:25:16.985 --> 00:25:19.465
Manager, someone is going in now.

00:25:20.305 --> 00:25:21.945
Okay, I'll handle it myself.

00:25:22.465 --> 00:25:23.905
Ms. Lin…

00:25:23.985 --> 00:25:26.945
I don't want to go in there.

00:25:27.025 --> 00:25:29.025
Ugh, Ms. Lin…

00:25:29.105 --> 00:25:31.185
Keep walking, Jane.

00:25:31.705 --> 00:25:33.465
Can I wait in the car?

00:25:34.985 --> 00:25:36.185
Ms. Lin! Ms. Lin!

00:25:38.185 --> 00:25:40.185
How could a secretary abandon her boss?

00:25:40.265 --> 00:25:42.905
We need to find out
whether it's a real ghost or a fake one.

00:25:43.425 --> 00:25:44.305
Hurry.

00:25:44.385 --> 00:25:45.825
Ms. Lin…

00:25:59.825 --> 00:26:01.105
Should we leave, Ms. Lin?

00:26:01.185 --> 00:26:02.825
It's getting ice-cold.

00:26:03.745 --> 00:26:05.585
You're so scared you're imagining things.

00:26:20.625 --> 00:26:21.505
Ms. Lin.

00:26:21.585 --> 00:26:23.105
Did you hear what I heard?

00:26:25.185 --> 00:26:26.225
I didn't hear anything.

00:26:27.145 --> 00:26:29.745
It was a child's laugh, wasn't it?

00:26:30.345 --> 00:26:32.665
Your ears are
playing tricks on you. Let's go.

00:26:42.425 --> 00:26:43.985
Ms. Lin!

00:26:44.065 --> 00:26:46.585
Both the sights
and the sounds are crystal clear.

00:26:46.665 --> 00:26:48.585
Let's leave this place, Ms. Lin.

00:26:48.665 --> 00:26:50.865
Believe it or not,
just don't disrespect it.

00:27:20.785 --> 00:27:21.745
Ms. Lin!

00:27:21.825 --> 00:27:23.185
A lady.

00:27:24.505 --> 00:27:25.505
A ghost lady!

00:27:26.665 --> 00:27:29.345
Jane. Jane.

00:27:45.785 --> 00:27:46.665
Oh.

00:27:53.545 --> 00:27:54.745
I'm out.

00:29:05.265 --> 00:29:06.865
A ghost! A ghost!

00:29:06.945 --> 00:29:08.585
You think you can run from me?

00:29:08.665 --> 00:29:10.345
Should I call the police?

00:29:15.665 --> 00:29:17.025
Oh?

00:29:22.105 --> 00:29:24.025
Can you not call the police?

00:29:25.305 --> 00:29:28.545
You should be talking to Mr. Pao
to find new opportunities for the staff

00:29:28.625 --> 00:29:30.225
instead of plotting immature tricks

00:29:30.305 --> 00:29:32.385
like a woman-child.

00:29:33.465 --> 00:29:34.665
Whoa.

00:29:35.865 --> 00:29:36.865
That hurts.

00:29:39.705 --> 00:29:41.305
I'm serious.

00:29:41.385 --> 00:29:42.905
You have my business card.

00:29:43.425 --> 00:29:45.745
Just call me and ask me
to help get your team jobs.

00:29:45.825 --> 00:29:47.505
I'm happy to help.

00:29:51.545 --> 00:29:53.985
You've probably worked
at a children's theme park for so long

00:29:54.065 --> 00:29:55.865
so you're only
thinking of childish solutions.

00:30:00.265 --> 00:30:01.705
What's wrong with you?

00:30:01.785 --> 00:30:03.505
Childish this, childish that.

00:30:03.585 --> 00:30:04.505
Why?

00:30:04.585 --> 00:30:07.585
A businesswoman like you has no
fond memories of the amusement park?

00:30:07.665 --> 00:30:10.225
That's why you have to take away
the children's happiness?

00:30:12.225 --> 00:30:16.105
Dad. Mom.

00:30:17.145 --> 00:30:22.745
Where are you? I want to go home now.

00:30:22.825 --> 00:30:25.945
Dad. Mom.

00:30:26.905 --> 00:30:28.305
Well, why so quiet?

00:30:28.825 --> 00:30:30.465
Why don't you continue?

00:30:33.305 --> 00:30:34.945
I've said everything I wanted to say.

00:30:56.985 --> 00:30:57.905
Alright.

00:30:57.985 --> 00:30:59.985
If I must die
in the line of duty for my boss…

00:31:24.225 --> 00:31:25.465
That's my shadow.

00:31:40.625 --> 00:31:42.185
Ms. Lin.

00:31:42.905 --> 00:31:44.465
Where are you?

00:31:45.065 --> 00:31:46.545
Ms. Lin.

00:31:49.425 --> 00:31:51.305
Just think about it.

00:31:51.385 --> 00:31:52.465
We're all grown-ups.

00:32:13.865 --> 00:32:14.745
Ms. Lin.

00:32:14.825 --> 00:32:16.345
Where are you?

00:32:17.705 --> 00:32:18.665
I'm here.

00:32:22.305 --> 00:32:23.305
Ms. Lin.

00:32:23.385 --> 00:32:24.625
If I wasn't worried about you,

00:32:24.705 --> 00:32:26.145
I wouldn't have dared come back.

00:32:27.105 --> 00:32:28.545
Let's hurry and get out of here.

00:32:28.625 --> 00:32:30.305
No need to be afraid. There are no ghosts.

00:32:30.385 --> 00:32:31.785
Someone staged it.

00:32:32.385 --> 00:32:34.145
-Really?
-Mhm.

00:32:34.985 --> 00:32:36.545
That's a relief, Ms. Lin.

00:32:36.625 --> 00:32:38.585
And who's playing tricks like this?

00:32:39.865 --> 00:32:41.145
Just troublemakers,

00:32:41.225 --> 00:32:43.225
the amusement park workers' kids.

00:32:44.025 --> 00:32:45.305
I sent them all home.

00:32:45.385 --> 00:32:47.105
They won't dare
to bother us again tonight.

00:32:48.185 --> 00:32:49.665
You're too bold, Ms. Lin.

00:32:49.745 --> 00:32:51.465
You should have called security first.

00:32:52.065 --> 00:32:54.185
You're lucky you weren't hurt.

00:32:56.545 --> 00:32:58.025
It was more like I hurt them.

00:32:58.105 --> 00:33:00.745
They could have come for me.

00:33:01.345 --> 00:33:02.865
But luckily, you were here in time.

00:33:04.985 --> 00:33:06.705
It's nothing, really.

00:33:07.225 --> 00:33:08.385
It shouldn't be a problem anymore.

00:33:08.465 --> 00:33:10.825
You can call the workers to come back.

00:33:10.905 --> 00:33:12.225
Oh, okay.

00:33:21.945 --> 00:33:23.425
What do I do?

00:33:23.945 --> 00:33:26.745
Mr. Pao doesn't seem to
want to fight anymore.

00:33:28.025 --> 00:33:29.185
And is Ms. Lin

00:33:29.705 --> 00:33:31.265
Sherlock Holmes or something?

00:33:31.345 --> 00:33:33.185
Always managing to see right through me.

00:33:49.905 --> 00:33:53.345
Mr. Pao told me
you have a younger brother named Ith.

00:33:59.025 --> 00:34:02.145
Bring your brother to see
the feng shui at my house sometime.

00:34:24.304 --> 00:34:26.105
Your son is really cute.

00:34:26.185 --> 00:34:27.465
He's my nephew.

00:34:28.065 --> 00:34:28.945
Nephew?

00:34:29.025 --> 00:34:30.665
Yes. He's my sister's son.

00:34:49.625 --> 00:34:51.385
Just think about it.

00:34:51.465 --> 00:34:52.545
We're all grown-ups.

00:35:01.265 --> 00:35:03.145
I need to change my plan.

00:35:39.785 --> 00:35:41.745
Did you order balloons, Ms. Lin?

00:35:41.825 --> 00:35:42.665
I didn't.

00:35:43.465 --> 00:35:45.425
Then it must have been
sent to the wrong house.

00:35:45.505 --> 00:35:47.465
Wait, Gib. Let me see it.

00:35:48.545 --> 00:35:49.425
Here, ma'am.

00:36:32.865 --> 00:36:34.465
We're not interested. We're in a rush.

00:36:34.985 --> 00:36:37.185
It won't take long.
Let's just take a look.

00:36:37.265 --> 00:36:38.865
Oh, didn't you say you're in a hurry?

00:36:40.865 --> 00:36:42.185
Taking a picture too?

00:36:42.265 --> 00:36:43.825
Do you still have time to change?

00:36:46.505 --> 00:36:48.425
There you go.

00:36:55.985 --> 00:36:57.865
Yeah. Okay.

00:36:57.945 --> 00:36:59.145
I think that's enough.

00:37:16.385 --> 00:37:17.945
Let's go, Ms. Lin.

00:37:30.225 --> 00:37:31.865
I don't think
it's been sent to the wrong house.

00:37:53.985 --> 00:37:55.905
FAMILYNEST LILIN
FOLLOW / MESSAGE

00:37:56.505 --> 00:37:58.025
Family Nest

00:37:58.105 --> 00:37:59.225
Lilin?

00:38:43.345 --> 00:38:46.305
INGINGPLAYPARK
FOLLOW BACK / MESSAGE

00:38:46.985 --> 00:38:48.425
Follow me back.

00:38:50.185 --> 00:38:52.465
What's taking you so long.

00:38:53.705 --> 00:38:55.545
Why aren't you following me back?

00:38:55.625 --> 00:38:56.985
FOLLOW BACK

00:38:57.065 --> 00:38:58.945
FOLLOWING

00:39:03.745 --> 00:39:05.585
Did you order this, Ms. Lin?

00:39:06.105 --> 00:39:07.385
Did they get the wrong person?

00:39:07.985 --> 00:39:08.825
There's no way.

00:39:08.905 --> 00:39:12.105
It specified the recipient's full name,
office floor, and position.

00:39:12.705 --> 00:39:14.185
Then it's mine.

00:39:16.145 --> 00:39:17.665
Can I have your LINE ID?

00:39:17.745 --> 00:39:19.545
I'm creating our LINE group.

00:39:19.625 --> 00:39:20.705
So silly.

00:39:23.185 --> 00:39:25.385
Did I do something silly, Ms. Lin?

00:39:25.985 --> 00:39:27.825
No, I wasn't talking about you.

00:39:27.905 --> 00:39:28.985
Thank you.

00:39:33.065 --> 00:39:34.505
Put it down.

00:39:35.465 --> 00:39:36.505
Yes.

00:39:40.945 --> 00:39:41.785
You can go.

00:39:43.185 --> 00:39:44.025
I'm going now.

00:39:44.105 --> 00:39:44.985
I'm going.

00:39:50.345 --> 00:39:52.225
What should I name the group?

00:39:59.785 --> 00:40:01.945
Is our secret group's name adorable?

00:40:02.025 --> 00:40:04.625
"Lin Ing In Love."

00:40:09.785 --> 00:40:10.865
I got you.

00:40:11.385 --> 00:40:13.225
The CEO has been reeled in.

00:40:14.305 --> 00:40:16.145
This is your new plan, isn't it?

00:40:17.345 --> 00:40:18.985
Always a scheme up your sleeve.

00:40:19.945 --> 00:40:22.265
You deserve a serious punishment.

00:40:30.985 --> 00:40:31.865
Hey.

00:40:33.065 --> 00:40:34.425
What am I doing?

00:40:51.385 --> 00:40:53.785
One adult pass
and one child pass, correct?

00:40:53.865 --> 00:40:54.785
Okay.

00:40:56.545 --> 00:40:57.705
Here you go.

00:40:57.785 --> 00:40:58.865
Thank you very much.

00:40:58.945 --> 00:40:59.905
Thank you.

00:41:54.825 --> 00:41:56.225
Oh, sorry.

00:42:20.465 --> 00:42:21.625
Let go of me!

00:42:25.745 --> 00:42:26.825
Ing.

00:42:36.225 --> 00:42:37.065
Come here.

00:42:37.705 --> 00:42:38.785
Where are you running to?

00:42:38.865 --> 00:42:40.785
We're husband and wife,
why can't we sleep together?

00:42:40.865 --> 00:42:41.905
Huh?

00:42:42.785 --> 00:42:44.065
Do I have to transition to be a woman?

00:42:48.665 --> 00:42:49.985
You can't run from me, Ing!

00:42:57.825 --> 00:42:59.505
-Ing.
-Don't come closer.

00:43:11.785 --> 00:43:13.745
NO ENTRY

00:43:38.385 --> 00:43:40.105
NO ENTRY

00:44:21.585 --> 00:44:23.985
I'll introduce you to Ms. Lin someday.

00:44:24.505 --> 00:44:26.105
You'll like her a lot.

00:44:28.185 --> 00:44:30.465
I think I've figured out your game plan.

00:44:30.985 --> 00:44:33.705
You're trying to change my mind.

00:44:33.785 --> 00:44:36.665
I admit, I'm really into you.

00:44:39.465 --> 00:44:40.385
Go for it, sis.

00:44:41.065 --> 00:44:42.665
Are you crazy?

00:44:42.745 --> 00:44:44.145
Isn't it too soon?

00:44:49.025 --> 00:44:49.825
I'm sorry.

00:44:49.905 --> 00:44:51.385
I'm sorry.

00:44:51.465 --> 00:44:53.945
She's already taken.

00:44:54.985 --> 00:44:57.665
So it's not just me, right?

00:46:54.385 --> 00:47:00.585
Subtitle translation by:
Anan Pratchayakul